{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"3b1af18218","title":"会见马里国家元首特拉奥雷时的谈话（节录）","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"5ebf73d859","index":0,"year":1973,"month":6,"day":22,"articleId":"3b1af18218","article":{}}],"tags":[{"name":"对外关系和政策","id":"2bffb53b5b","type":"主题"},{"name":"对话","id":"314ad57c4d","type":"文稿类型"},{"name":"关键人物文稿","id":"c20d333791","type":"文稿大类"},{"name":"毛泽东","id":"dd2b275f6c","type":"人物"},{"name":"毛泽东","id":"e2305b9e63","type":"主题"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji51","name":"毛泽东全集第51卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/51-OCR.pdf","articles":[],"comments":[],"contents":[],"pages":[]},{"id":"wenku","name":"中国文化大革命文库（第一版）","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":"","articles":[],"comments":[],"contents":[],"pages":[]}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji51":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"e22203f556","type":"title","text":"会见马里国家元首特拉奥雷时的谈话（节录）","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji51","articleId":"3b1af18218","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"90680ba05d","type":"paragraph","text":"我们都是叫作第三世界，就是叫作发展中的国家。你不要看我国有什么展览会啊，其实啊，是一个很穷的国家。我说，Isay（英文：我说），越穷越好！就会革命啊。西方国家呢，不大行了。","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji51","articleId":"3b1af18218","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"53416508fa","type":"paragraph","text":"无论怎么样，这些西方资本主义国家是创造了文化，创造了科学，创造了工业。现在我们第三世界可以利用他们的科学、工业、文化——包括语言一—的好的部分。","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji51","articleId":"3b1af18218","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"5dd26bd0db","type":"paragraph","text":"1973年6月22日，毛泽东会见马里共和国总理特拉奥雷。","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji51","articleId":"3b1af18218","publication":{},"article":{}}],"page":{"start":413,"end":413}},"wenku":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"9b6de51e39","type":"paragraph","text":"（外交部绝密文件，文特43）","index":3,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"3b1af18218","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"9c6ccef2bd","type":"paragraph","text":"无论怎么样，这些西方资本主义国家是创造了文化，创造了科学，创造了工业。现在我们第三世界可以利用他们的科学、工业、文化──包括语言──的好的部分。","index":2,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"3b1af18218","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"df357a47ab","type":"title","text":"会见马里国家元首特拉奥雷时的谈话（节录）","index":0,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"3b1af18218","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"ebc28c048c","type":"paragraph","text":"我们都是叫作第三世界，就是叫做发展中的国家。你不要看中国有什么展览会啊，其实啊，是一个很穷的国家。我说，I SAY（英文：我说），越穷越好！就会革命啊。西方国家呢，不大行了。","index":1,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"3b1af18218","publication":{},"article":{}}],"page":{"start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}